    "Lastly, unlabeled accounts are ranked by their credibility scores for evaluation.",
    "In the next subsections, we present several methods to infer account credibility based on trust in accounts or sources.",
    "In each case, we evaluate centrality-based methods and an embedding algorithm.",
    "Centrality-based methods are less sophisticated but more efficient and interpretable.",
    "Trust in accountsWe describe algorithms to calculate an account's credibility by leveraging their trust in other accounts."
